If you want to set a special skin for the emailed html version of your
newsletter, you must set this property (through the ZMI) on your newsletter
folder : 
 Name : mailskin
 Type : string
 Value : name_of_your_skin

To customize the subscription message, set this property :
 Name : subscription_message
 Type : text
 Value : The text that requests the user to confirm its subscription
replying to this message

To customize the confirmation message, set this property :
 Name : confirmation_message
 Type : text
 Value : The text that welcomes the user

To customize the unsubscription message, set this property :
 Name : unsubscription_message
 Type : text
 Value : The text that requests the user to confirm its unsubscription
replying to this message

To customize the removal confirmation message, set this property :
 Name : rconfirmation_message
 Type : text
 Value : The text that says good bye to the user


If you want a special release (i.e. the latest one) to be delivered to new
subscribers, set this property :
 Name : welcome_release
 Type : text
 Value : Name of the Publication containing the release
IMPORTANT : If you set welcome_release, you must allow "Anonymous" to "List
Folder Contents" on your newsletter folder

